{"tid":2124132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"筲箕灣愛蝶灣3保安箍區議員頸搶電話","createTime":"2020-07-25T07:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T06:28:53.000Z","uid":292911,"like":477,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":144,"replies":[{"pid":"af25a7ba849fd70c7d5e1865c10449e90d8d7a72","tid":2124132,"uid":292911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"【愛蝶灣管理處拒絕公開疫情資訊  我被三人箍頸並搶電話】<br />\n<br />\n收到 #愛蝶灣 居民通知，懷疑有確診個案人士與管理公司夜更保安有接觸。因此我馬上到管理處理解。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，三位保安對我百般阻撓，甚至一齊向我動粗，箍我頸、搶我電話，試圖逃避追問。<br />\n<br />\n盡快為居民求證，是我份內之事，但管理處不積極處理之餘，更向我動手，我表達極度憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n但我會繼續為居民服務，任何惡勢力都無法阻止！<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/566652983808012/posts/968200950319878/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F566652983808012%2Fposts%2F968200950319878%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=79b115e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/566652983808012/posts/968200950319878/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n投訴師進場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />- 富城集團<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.urban.com.hk/chi/contact/01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urban.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fcontact%2F01.htm&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=dc802f3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.urban.com.hk/chi/contact/01.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3619b56e654fb7ea415ff42918498e571b77869f","tid":2124132,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cda5c7c7ba3902f6a2309b915260025b66dc9ce","tid":2124132,"uid":252142,"like":81,"dislike":13,"score":68,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9574d84e17c717cff4d8695d102188ffd1ef542","tid":2124132,"uid":184261,"like":10