:0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"跟進番<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位關心，我人沒有大礙。我已向富城管理公司總部反映，要求管理公司核對所有保安住址有否與確診大廈地址重疊。無論有或沒有，都要在屋苑當眼處，及每座大堂貼通告通知住戶。<br />\n<br />\n有街坊消息謂2、3座夜更保安與確診人士為同一大廈（非密切接觸者），現正進行測試，兩天後有結果。此消息尚未有管理處核實，請各街坊留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/566652983808012/posts/968227230317250/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F566652983808012%2Fposts%2F968227230317250%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=43ffa8c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/566652983808012/posts/968227230317250/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"699b6198fc8633d35e5757d0ceb53cd859c15e89","tid":2124132,"uid":3873,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"愛蝶灣業主委員會主席好似仲係林其東，即係上屆區議員，上次初選見佢辦事處門口貼咗張香港再出發的poster"},{"pid":"a5603610e7c02e86f90edea5ff050c6b6e0ac802","tid":2124132,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"富城應該係新世界"},{"pid":"d5a8f1f2fdae24e21022289d036ff610743e3b6c","tid":2124132,"uid":338422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"咁都得 你保安黎咋"},{"pid":"724f7bb16fdd12f0ca93f43990b274d06f893627","tid":2124132,"uid":292911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699b6198fc8633d35e5757d0ceb53cd859c15e89","tid":2124132,"uid":3873,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"愛蝶灣業主委員會主席好似仲係林其東，即係上屆區議員，上次初選見佢辦事處門口貼咗張香港再出發的poster"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />武肺再出發呀佢"},{"pid":"1dc65c679c6d681da80faed82615eea9a63ff29d","tid":2124132,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class